    feat(QuantumInfo): prove qRelativeEnt_joint_convexity (joint convexity of Umegaki relative entropy)
    
    Closes the sorry in QuantumInfo/Entropy/Relative.lean by proving joint convexity of the
    Umegaki quantum relative entropy from the already-proved sandwiched-Rényi joint convexity
    (alpha->1). The theorem is placed in DPI.lean (which imports Relative.lean) to reach that
    machinery without an import cycle. #print axioms: only propext/Classical.choice/Quot.sound.
    
